通龐貝奧講嘅嘢又係假？？？我覺得最緊要大家應該要有批判性思考，唔好比軸心國嘅概念同文化入侵大家嘅思想<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWANXtRzZtHbqCgcAXQHq9iqDyDDqptE24Extz2xDcbGL?filename=5nvyNJq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nvyNJq.jpg&h=6bf32f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">1.）美國國務卿龐貝奧受大紀元邀請做訪問</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【#大紀元唔可信】Pompeo接受《大紀元》專訪<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2360412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2360412</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">2.）大紀元奪美國app store 第一媒體下載量</span></span><br />\n<br />\n英文版大紀元奪美國本月app store 第一媒體類下載量<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2297542\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2297542</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">3.）美國總統川普向超過7000萬支持者宣傳大紀元</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[突發]美國總統轉載大紀元新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2308034\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2308034</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n連美國總統都有份宣傳，宜家Trump 七千萬支持者爭住下載英文大紀元app<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbBC8fHNzSsssUzwJb5H1pHM73G8BoSrM1ZAp8iuzQRS4?filename=v3dKjrL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv3dKjrL.jpg&h=453fac5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYQuaxvmzERu2XpwWzyuPACZ57QKpW623YUn9GRsV5Axb?filename=1YyaZrM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1YyaZrM.jpg&h=073af4f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQkzS4aMuLzNgzdhopJn2g66e9bpD3pk3LtvQSGdppip9?filename=wMiBUZ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwMiBUZ7.jpg&h=2c2b76bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5059d5a51791d069ccd51e83d09d6427669ae3e8","tid":2495814,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c081f25dae55d3eb5fa5786468dee487719f426f","tid":